<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/board-of-trustees-of-the-royal-botanic-gardens-kew> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Board of Trustees of the Royal Botanic Gardens Kew is responsible for ensuring that Kew Gardens operates within the guidelines set out by government, and secures maximum value for money. Board of Trustees of the Royal Botanic Gardens Kew is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Environment, Food & Rural Affairs ."@en .
